{"tid":1842901,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平雲南","createTime":"2020-01-26T03:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T06:35:55.000Z","uid":29188,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f525d99961fb82080df7c034b7a17ebbe48df93f","tid":1842901,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:31:32.000Z","msg":"黨和國家領導人習近平到雲南視察，雲南省政府為了贊美習近平，請來一位知名畫家，要畫一幅油畫，名為《習近平在雲南》。<br />\n畫家不願意為習近平作畫，但在雲南省政府的威逼下，還是畫了。<br />\n<br />\n當這幅畫交到雲南省省委書記手裡的時候，書記立刻傻眼了。<br />\n<br />\n問：「這棟樓是什麼？」<br />\n<br />\n畫家答：「武漢市某人民醫院。」<br />\n<br />\n「這畫上兩名穿白衣服的人是誰？」<br />\n<br />\n「武漢醫生。」<br />\n<br />\n「躺在擔架上的人是誰？」<br />\n<br />\n「肺炎患者。」<br />\n<br />\n「那習近平總書記在哪？」<br />\n<br />\n「習近平在雲南。」"},{"pid":"89d99554b4cbef89a1962a20c722d846e7ce17f7","tid":1842901,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d92f291d4fb11fbe562baee02e29db694db5f2","tid":1842901,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:41:14.000Z","msg":"波蘭的列寧"},{"pid":"5f6e8a3b07c93cc1dc3c253225c8ee642cd327cd","tid":1842901,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:23:24.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"52e4e316840859e0486afb1fc848971d23c03d32","tid":1842901,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/pl--CLIzcN4/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fpl--CLIzcN4%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=1e14afed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"439f037fff959bbedc76093a6c2110a907ba414d","tid":1842901,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:34:46.000Z","msg":"以為去到雲南就無事?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雖遠必誅</span></span><img src=\